Class CSVWriterMetadata<Model>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.writer.CSVWriterMetadata<Model>
  • Type Parameters:
    Model - type of the field mapping descriptor.

    public final class CSVWriterMetadata<Model>
extends Object
    Represents the meta-data used to tell a CSVWriterFactoryImpl how to build and configure the related CSVWriters.
